sa:

  → development/languages/Perl/modules/Tree/Create/DepthFirst allows to create a `Tree::Simple` tree by adding its nodes in the same sequence (or order) which
  they would/ill be returned if the tree is traversed depth first.

  → development/languages/Perl/modules/Tree/Parser[`Tree::Parser`] can be used to parse text with a »tree structure« and create a `Tree::Simple` object from it.

  → development/languages/Perl/modules/Tree/Simple/View/HTML creates `<UL> … <LI> … </UL>` html text from a `Tree::Simple` object.

  → development/languages/Perl/modules/index[Perl modules]

